'''Voshan Containers''' was a freight shipping company that operated during the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. They shipped goods along the [[Corellian Run/Legends|Corellian Run]]. The company was easily identified by its bright orange livery.

==History==
One of their [[Starship/Legends|ships]] was involved in an [[Mission to the Corellian-Perlemian Intersection|incident]] with an [[TIV Z590/1|unmarked]] [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] [[Traffic Interdiction Vessel|traffic interdiction vessel]] at the [[Corellian Run/Legends|Corellian]]&ndash;[[Perlemian node|Perlemian]] [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] intersection 367 days after the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|Battle of Geonosis]].

